Version 0.1.10
* Ported to Python 3 and PyGObject (by actionless)
* Metacity keybindings removed
* New translations
  - Finnish
  - Hebrew
  - Indonesian
  - Kurdish Sorani
  - Norwegian Bokmål
* Updated translations
  - Breton
  - Czech
  - French
  - Galego
  - Galician
  - Greek
  - Japanese
  - Kannada
  - Lithuanian
  - Romanian
  - Sardinian
  - Slovak
  - Swedish
  - Turkish
  - Chinese (Traditional)

Version 0.1.9
* Support xrandr 1.5.0
* New translations:
  - Albanian
* Updated translations

